# MySQL Initialization Scripts
#
# Any .sql or .sh files placed here will be executed automatically
# when the MySQL container starts for the FIRST TIME only.
#
# Use this for:
# - Creating additional databases
# - Setting up initial users/permissions
# - Running initial schema migrations
# - Importing seed data
#
# Files are executed in alphabetical order.
# Prefix with numbers like 01-, 02- to control execution order.
